# README Maintenance

After making code changes, check if README.md needs updating:

- **Update README.md** when changes affect:
  - Installation or setup instructions
  - Usage examples or CLI commands
  - Configuration options
  - Dependencies (requirements.txt, package.json, etc.)
  - API or interface changes
  - Feature additions or removals

- **Do NOT create new documentation files** (no new .md files, no separate docs folder)

- Keep all documentation in the existing README.md
